These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
There 2 different types of food: watermelon, apricot
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not the person eating apricot##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | apricot   | watermelon  |
| Sport   | sailing | ice-hockey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
There 2 different types of food: avocado, mango
2 different pets are kept: cat, rat
1. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
2. the owner of the cat is not the person eating mango##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | avocado | mango      |
| Pet    | cat  | rat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-3::.
