.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-5::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: thriller, mystery
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: weightlifting, skiing
1. the person watching mystery movies is not the person who's sport is skiing##6
2. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is skiing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller  | mystery |
| Sport         | skiing | weightlifting      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-6::.
