.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-7::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  security-guard, chef
2 different pets are kept: mouse, goldfish
1. the security-guard is in an odd position##4
2. the security-guard is not the owner of the goldfish##6

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1      |       2       |
| Job   | security-guard | chef |
| Pet   | mouse       | goldfish       |

